  "texts": [
    "For example, in live football broadcasting, there is a need to classify player poses for the purpose of automating camera control.",
    "This can assist upcoming phases of a game or event, leading to better organization of shots.",
    "Considering the variation of background clutter (e.g., from a crowd, grass, dynamic advertisement banners, etc.",
    "), object detection presents significant challenges.",
    "Location can be identified by either pixel-level contouring around the object's edge or by a bounding box."
  ],
